    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269472</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_050_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ここが……
&lt;Red&gt;ヴァルハラ&lt;White&gt;……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This is...Valhalla? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269580</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_050_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたしたちの時代の
&lt;Red&gt;ヴァルハラ&lt;White&gt;と
ずいぶん違うね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Our era's Valhalla is completely different from this... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269644</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_050_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうした？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What happened? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269756</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_050_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いえ……ずいぶん、
小さな町……っていうか
村なんだなって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Nothing...everything's ok... It's just we didn't expect 
this to be such a small town—I mean village. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270072</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_050_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もともと差別で街を
追い出された人や</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Originally there were a lot of people here, but... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270072</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_050_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>戦争で街をなくした人が
急ごしらえで作った村だしな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>After a war it's only natural that
most of them left the village. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270140</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_050_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうなんだ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So that's why... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270288</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_050_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>とりあえず、
私はバジルを
呼んでくる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>At any rate, I'll go call Basil. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270288</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_050_050_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>君たちは適当に
村の中を見て回っててくれ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You can take a look around here in the meantime. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
